cleaned_text: We offer online scheduling for massage therapy and Reiki. Insurance is not accepted for massages. Please review our fees prior to booking. If you need assistance scheduling any appointment, please call us at 201-608-2377. Note: Our full schedule is not online. If you do not see the day/time, therapist, or massage type you are looking for, please contact us directly at 201-608-2377. We will do our best to accommodate your request.
